<template>
    <component v-bind:is="components" />
    <button @click="components = 'TheOne'">TheOne</button>
    <button @click="components = 'TheTwo'">TheTwo</button>
</template>
<script>
import TheOne from "./components/TheOne.vue";
import TheTwo from "./components/TheTwo.vue";
export default {
    name: "TheAll",
    components: {
        TheOne,
        TheTwo,
    },
    data() {
        return {
            components: "TheOne"
        }
    }
}
</script>
